## Retained Findings
- retained issues focused on `StakingRewards` reward-accounting and payout solvency: emissions can be promised without reserved mint capacity, and undistributed / canceled emissions still consume the farm’s lifetime reward budget
- token-behavior compatibility was also retained: the staking ledger can become insolvent with fee-on-transfer or rebasing staking tokens
- one lower-confidence retained issue covered arithmetic/storage limits: `uint96` reward-supply tracking can wrap and overbook rewards when token caps exceed the 96-bit range
